page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI's embeddings API for document search with the BillSum dataset
chunk_content: Clean up resourcesIf you created an Azure OpenAI resource solely for completing this tutorial and want to clean up and remove an Azure OpenAI resource, you'll need to delete your deployed models, and then delete the resource or associated resource group if it's dedicated to your test resource. Deleting the resource group also deletes any other resources associated with it.- Portal- Azure CLI
